attributes.title: n o
attributes.review: ever since i downloaded this app my vision has been enhanced in a way to only be able to see barry b benson. at first i didn’t think it would be all that bad but the more i sneeze, the more barry b benson appears. he’s everywhere, even in my dreams. some say this would be a luxury but no. my dreams were my only safe space and it’s ruined. my dog is typing this out for me since the only thing i can see right now is that goddamn bee. i have become unmotivated to do anything anymore, not even spend time with the ones i love. i have been flooded with thoughts that only made me worry more. my therapist said that my vision has taken a toll on my depression and anxiety. and because of this, i can only drink apple juice. the only time i can see things other than barry b benson is when im watching the bee movie. ive watched it over 12 times this month. i don’t recommend this app. 0/10000000000000
